Definition: a tropical floating aquatic plant having spikes of large blue flowers
Example: troublesome in clogging waterways especially in southern United States
Synonyms: water_orchid, Eichhornia_crassipes, Eichhornia_spesiosa, aquatic_plant, genus_Eichhornia, m, a, tropical, floating, aquatic, plant, having, spikes, of, large, blue, flowers, troublesome, in, clogging, waterways, especially, southern, United, States
Category: noun.plant
